                            <comment id="16147809" author="oliver.heger@t-online.de" created="Wed, 30 Aug 2017 18:44:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you for the report. I will have a look.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16149178" author="oliver.heger@t-online.de" created="Thu, 31 Aug 2017 16:04:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in SVN in revision 1806820.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The root cause of the problem was that configuration nodes without children (as is the case for an empty section) were not recognized as section nodes. This has been fixed now.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks again.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
